Title: Ghost condensates in Yang-Mills theories in the Landau gauge
Authors: V.E.R. Lemes, M.S. Sarandy, and S.P. Sorella
Comments: 24 pages, references added, final version to appear in Ann. of Phys
\\
  Ghost condensates of dimension two are analysed in pure SU(N) Yang-Mills
theories by combining the local composite operators technique with the
algebraic BRST renormalization.
